variable.name: PCR_x
variable.description: Protein Catabolic Rate g/kg/d with FHS weight
variable.comment: This variable was calculated using weight variable from FHS Offspring Exam 9 or OMNI 1 Exam 4: PCR = (6.25*(UUN24+(WEIGHT_KG*0.031)))/(WEIGHT_KG).
